My favorite colors are warm tones and black.
I enjoy knitting and crochet.
I like a variety of music with preference to psychedelia, metal, harsh noise, and drum and bass.
My drawing programs of choice are Paint Tool Sai and Adobe Photoshop CS6.
My traditional mediums of choice are colored pencils and acrylic.
